{"id":232956328,"title":"去泰國請佛牌","content":"我是佛牌小白，之前看到很有眼緣的必達才開始有稍微研究。\n今天去了蘇泰寺想說去找找有沒有不錯的佛牌可以入手當我的第二面，進去佛牌小屋後玲瑯滿目的佛牌讓我不知道該從何看起，\n實在太多沒有看過也不敢亂入手，只好以五大古佛為方向尋找，結果一問之下店裡有一尊南帕雅\n（店內沒有其他三尊古佛，有蠻多崇迪，但是已經有在台灣佛牌社團上看上一面因此就沒考慮崇迪）\n所以我就入手了一尊南帕雅。有請販售人員將師父名稱與出處寫於紙上，也有請泰國友人幫忙將字打於手機上\nนางพญา ลด.แย็ม วัดตะเคียบ\n分別為名稱、師傅、出處\n但是我搜尋找了一下找不太到什麼資訊，有沒有人可以為我解答🙏\nhttps://i.imgur.com/mzhS0c2.jpg","excerpt":"我是佛牌小白，之前看到很有眼緣的必達才開始有稍微研究。今天去了蘇泰寺想說去找找有沒有不錯的佛牌可以入手當我的第二面，進去佛牌小屋後玲瑯滿目的佛牌讓我不知道該從何看起，實在太多沒有看過也不敢亂入手，只好","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"37a78696-f6a6-48ec-a19f-688f799a2aed","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-25T13:45:02.320Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T13:46:15.470Z","commentCount":13,"likeCount":1,"tags":[],"topics":["佛牌","泰國"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"靈異","forumAlias":"marvel","school":"守","department":"sean860511","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/mzhS0c2.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"2667874f-bdb9-4de7-8694-8bfc2cf3f5b0","url":"https://i.imgur.com/mzhS0c2l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/mzhS0c2l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/mzhS0c2l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-25T13:45:02.320Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T13:46:15.470Z"},{"id":"2667874f-bdb9-4de7-8694-8bfc2cf3f5b0","url":"https://i.imgur.com/mzhS0c2.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/mzhS0c2","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/mzhS0c2l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-25T13:45:02.320Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T13:46:15.470Z"}],"postAvatar":""}